trans-unit.source: Provides a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en samling <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartTransformerCollection class is a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects, typically used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> object to manage a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects for a connection.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartTransformerCollection er en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>objekter, vanligvis brukes av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>objektet til å administrere et sett med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>objekter for en tilkobling.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>

trans-unit.source: The transformers related to a Web Parts connection can be retrieved through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.Transformers%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Transformeringer relatert til en webdeler tilkobling kan hentes via den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.Transformers%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.Transformers%2A>
